==English==
===Adjective===
'''qualifies'''

#[[satisfying|Satisfying]] the the requirements.
#:''He '''qualifies''' for the award as far as time worked is concerned, but we can't give it to him because he had too many absences.''
#[[modifying|Modifying]], limiting or restricting.
#:''The final sentence of the will '''qualifies''' the bequest so it is only given for one year.''